{"tid":836624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美諧星 Bill Cosby 面臨三至十年監禁","createTime":"2018-09-25T19:53:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T23:39:44.000Z","uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5fc709117fd1bb1bb6f1e8cf705b17d221343fc2","tid":836624,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T19:53:16.000Z","msg":"好野，用藥咁低庄啦嗱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n========================<br />\n&bull;Bill Cosby, 81, was sentenced on Tuesday to three to 10 years in state prison<br />\n&bull;Judge Steven O'Neill handed down Cosby's sentence on Tuesday afternoon<br />\n&bull;Comedian was also fined $25,000 and ordered to pay prosecution costs <br />\n&bull;Cosby sat back in his chair with his head on a headrest as the sentence was read<br />\n&bull;He will appear on a sex-offender registry after the judge earlier declared he is a 'sexually violent predator'<br />\n&bull;Cosby's sentencing comes five months after he was convicted for drugging and sexually assaulting Andrea Constand at his Philadelphia home in 2004 <br />\n&bull;Prosecutors were seeking a sentence of five to 10 years in prison <br />\n&bull;His lawyers asked for house arrest, saying he is too old to do time in prison<br />\n&bull;His wife of 54 years, Camille, was not in court during Cosby's sentencing <br />\n&bull;A psychologist testified on Monday in court that Cosby had a disorder which makes him inclined to sleep with non-consenting women <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/25/20/50A9348900000578-0-image-a-76_1537902643947.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F20%2F50A9348900000578-0-image-a-76_1537902643947.jpg&h=0b089d9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Bill Cosby was sentenced to three to 10 years in state prison on Tuesday for drugging and molesting a woman in Philadelphia in 2004. He was handcuffed and escorted from the courtroom carrying his walking stick<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/25/20/50A9534A00000578-6205839-image-m-88_1537903932945.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F20%2F50A9534A00000578-6205839-image-m-88_1537903932945.jpg&h=722d3c31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/25/20/50A927CC00000578-6205839-image-m-78_1537902756226.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F20%2F50A927CC00000578-6205839-image-m-78_1537902756226.jpg&h=44286f8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Cosby's punishment came at the end of a two-day hearing at which the judge also declared Cosby a 'sexually violent predator'<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/25/20/50A92D0C00000578-6205839-image-m-84_1537903213084.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F20%2F50A92D0C00000578-6205839-image-m-84_1537903213084.jpg&h=875ebd54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Victim Andrea Constand emerged from the courtroom smiling on Tuesday after Cosby was jailed for drugging and molesting her at his Philadelphia home in 2004<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/25/20/50A92F8100000578-6205839-image-m-86_1537903317579.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F20%2F50A92F8100000578-6205839-image-m-86_1537903317579.jpg&h=6b6ab568&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Andrea Constand embraced Janice Dickinson, a woman who has also accused Cosby of assault, in the hallways of the court following his sentencing<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/25/17/50A75DB400000578-6205839-image-a-43_1537893489094.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F17%2F50A75DB400000578-6205839-image-a-43_1537893489094.jpg&h=94579826&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Judge Steven O'Neill (above) declared on Tuesday that Cosby is a 'sexually violent predator' when he sentenced the 81-year-old comedian for drugging and molesting a woman at his suburban Philadelphia home in 2004<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/25/18/50A76B9C00000578-6205839-image-a-45_1537895262666.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F18%2F50A76B9C00000578-6205839-image-a-45_1537895262666.jpg&h=9b20f2e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Former model Janice Dickinson raised her fist in the air as she left the courtroom on Tuesday. She is among the dozens of women to accuse Cosby of sexual assault<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/03/30/21/4AAEC53700000578-0-image-a-12_1522441058457.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F03%2F30%2F21%2F4AAEC53700000578-0-image-a-12_1522441058457.jpg&h=cd171e68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/03/30/21/4AAEB5C900000578-0-Janice_Baker_Kinney-a-10_1522441058453.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F03%2F30%2F21%2F4AAEB5C900000578-0-Janice_Baker_Kinney-a-10_1522441058453.jpg&h=d7b46724&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Janice Baker-Kinney<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/03/30/21/4AAEB5DF00000578-0-Janice_Dickinson_in_1982-a-6_1522441048021.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F03%2F30%2F21%2F4AAEB5DF00000578-0-Janice_Dickinson_in_1982-a-6_1522441048021.jpg&h=84b94801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Janice Dickinson in 1982<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/03/30/21/4AAEB38C00000578-0-image-a-2_1522441047614.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F03%2F30%2F21%2F4AAEB38C00000578-0-image-a-2_1522441047614.jpg&h=2b5dfa35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/03/30/21/4AAEB61B00000578-0-Chelan_Lasha_in_1986-a-7_1522441048078.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F03%2F30%2F21%2F4AAEB61B00000578-0-Chelan_Lasha_in_1986-a-7_1522441048078.jpg&h=ef83d0c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Chelan Lasha in 1986<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/03/30/21/4AAEB59D00000578-0-Lisa_Loote_Lublin_in_1989-a-5_1522441047981.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F03%2F30%2F21%2F4AAEB59D00000578-0-Lisa_Loote_Lublin_in_1989-a-5_1522441047981.jpg&h=ff07e60f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Lisa-Loote Lublin in 1989<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/03/30/21/4AAEB37400000578-0-Heidi_Thomas_in_1984-a-4_1522441047784.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F03%2F30%2F21%2F4AAEB37400000578-0-Heidi_Thomas_in_1984-a-4_1522441047784.jpg&h=f966fc9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Heidi Thomas in 1984<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2018/09/25/8195292565516798229/1024x576_MP4_8195292565516798229.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideos.dailymail.co.uk%2Fvideo%2Fmol%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F8195292565516798229%2F1024x576_MP4_8195292565516798229.mp4&d=QPh9qvvmeiGxVTY%2FFfJyqpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=5e1ca625\" target=\"_blank\">https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2018/09/25/8195292565516798229/102